<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AIScore Identitas Report</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .summary {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .personal-info, .result-section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .personal-info table, .result-section table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .personal-info table td, .result-section table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .score {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .score .score-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 20px;
            background-color: #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .score .score-bar .fill {
            height: 100%;
            width: 92%; /* 92% score */
            background-color: #4caf50;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .images {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .images img {
            max-width: 48%;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>AISCORE IDENTITAS REPORT</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="summary">
            <p>Hasil dari AISCORE-IDENTITAS 92% cocok dengan informasi yang ditampilkan. Face recognition/Kecocokan KTP yang di Upload dengan hasil verifikasi atau foto selfie 92% cocok, dan Optical Character Recognition (OCR)/Kecocokan informasi yang diberikan dengan hasil verifikasi 92% cocok.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="personal-info">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>NIK</td>
                    <td>32041521243</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Nama</td>
                    <td>Bagus 1</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Jenis Kelamin</td>
                    <td>Laki - Laki</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Alamat</td>
                    <td>Jl. Raya Cendudu</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Tempat Tanggal Lahir</td>
                    <td>Jakarta, 17 Januari 1985</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Agama</td>
                    <td>Islam</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Status Perkawinan</td>
                    <td>Kawin</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Pekerjaan</td>
                    <td>Karyawan</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Kewarganegaraan</td>
                    <td>WNI</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="result-section">
            <h3>Hasil Scan Upload</h3>
            <div class="images">
                <img src="ktp_image.png" alt="Hasil Scan KTP">
                <img src="selfie_image.png" alt="Hasil Verifikasi">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="score">
            <h3>Nilai AISCORE-IDENTITAS</h3>
            <div class="score-bar">
                <div class="fill"></div>
            </div>
            <p>92% (Sangat Baik)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Hasil AISCORE-IDENTITAS: 92%</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
